text: Agape is an awesome service that gives you a place when there's no where else to turn to. They have really, really nice foster parents like a foster mom or a foster mom and dad. text: This place is The worst possible place any kid should ever go to. I would never leave my kids in this place but my kids know some kids that live here and they have reported that the parents have pulled one of the kids out from under his bed causing him to hit his head and others have just blatantly thrown him out of his bed.
